"title": "5156: hand",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5156: hand",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Associated in Scripture with various activities, the hand symbolises particularly power and strength. Jesus Christ's hands often bring healing and blessing.</p>\n<h2>The hand as part of the physical body</h2>\n<h3>Hands used for physical work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">1TH 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:42\">GEN 31:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:7\">DEU 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:10\">JOB 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:17\">PSA 90:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:11\">ECC 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:34\">ACT 20:34</a></p>\n<h3>Hands used for praying</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:29\">EXO 9:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:38\">1KI 8:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:29\">2CH 6:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:12-2Chr6:13\">2CH 6:12–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:5\">EZR 9:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:2\">PSA 77:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:9\">PSA 88:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:8\">1TI 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Hands used in clapping</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:12\">2KI 11:12</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:1\">PSA 47:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:8\">PSA 98:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:12\">ISA 55:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:23\">JOB 27:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:15\">LAM 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:6\">EZK 25:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:19\">NAM 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Hands used for carrying weapons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:4\">JER 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:29\">NUM 22:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:17\">NUM 35:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:13\">JOS 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10\">1SA 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:11\">2KI 11:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:10\">2CH 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:1-Ezek9:2\">EZK 9:1–9:2</a></p>\n<h3>Hands used for writing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:11\">GAL 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:19\">1CH 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:24\">DAN 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:22\">ROM 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:18\">COL 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:17\">2TH 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:19\">PHM 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Hands as a means of assistance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:25\">MAT 9:25</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:41\">MRK 5:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:54\">LUK 8:54</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:31\">PSA 109:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:12\">ISA 63:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:6\">LAM 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:27\">MRK 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:7\">ACT 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:41\">ACT 9:41</a></p>\n<h3>Hands used in making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:19\">2CH 32:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:29\">DEU 31:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:18\">2KI 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:17\">2KI 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:25\">2CH 34:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:41\">ACT 7:41</a></p>\n<h3>Idle hands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:18\">ECC 10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:10\">PRO 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4\">PRO 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:25\">PRO 21:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:33\">PRO 24:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:5\">ECC 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:6\">ECC 11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Right and left hands</h2>\n<h3>Right hand as the place of honour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:19\">1KI 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:13-Gen48:14\">GEN 48:13–48:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr6:39\">1CH 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:24\">JER 22:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:33-Matt25:34\">MAT 25:33–25:34</a></p>\n<h3>Significant uses of the left hand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:16\">JDG 20:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:13-Gen48:14\">GEN 48:13–48:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:15\">JDG 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:21\">JDG 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:2\">1CH 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:3\">EZK 39:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3\">MAT 6:3</a></p>\n<h2>Symbolic uses of the hand</h2>\n<h3>The hand as a symbol of power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:2\">JOB 30:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:39-Deut32:40\">DEU 32:39–32:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:12\">1KI 11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:6\">ISA 47:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:15\">DAN 9:15</a></p>\n<h3>The hand as a symbol of violence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:2\">PSA 58:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:17\">JOB 16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:21\">JOB 31:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:17\">PRO 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:3\">ISA 59:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:6\">ISA 59:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:45\">EZK 23:45</a></p>\n<h3>Clean hands as a symbol of innocence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:6-Deut21:7\">DEU 21:6–21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:21\">2SA 22:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:20\">PSA 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:9\">JOB 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:30\">JOB 22:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:6\">PSA 26:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13\">PSA 73:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:24\">MAT 27:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Limp hands as a symbol of paralysing fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:7\">EZK 21:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:3\">JOB 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:7\">ISA 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:3\">ISA 35:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer47:3\">JER 47:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:17-Ezek7:18\">EZK 7:17–7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:16\">ZEP 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Hands as a symbol of temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8\">MAT 18:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22\">GEN 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:8\">EZK 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:17\">EZK 18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:30\">MAT 5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43\">MRK 9:43</a></p>\n<h2>Hands used in making agreements</h2>\n<h3>Striking hands in pledge</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:19\">EZR 10:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:1\">PRO 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:15\">PRO 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:18\">PRO 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:26\">PRO 22:26</a></p>\n<h3>Symbolic actions in oath taking</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:22\">GEN 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:2\">GEN 24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:9\">GEN 24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:29\">GEN 47:29</a></p>\n<h3>Joining hands in partnership or fellowship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:15\">2KI 10:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:6\">ISA 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:5\">HOS 7:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:9\">GAL 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of hands</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:5\">1SA 19:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg12:3\">JDG 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:21\">1SA 28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:14\">JOB 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:109\">PSA 119:109</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:8\">ISA 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Hands of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's hands used in healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:40\">LUK 4:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:3\">MAT 8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:41\">MRK 1:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:13\">LUK 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18\">MAT 9:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:23\">MRK 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:5\">MRK 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:32-Mark7:33\">MRK 7:32–7:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:13\">LUK 13:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's hands used in blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:50\">LUK 24:50</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's hands were pierced</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:27\">JHN 20:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:16\">PSA 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:37\">JHN 19:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:40\">LUK 24:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:25\">JHN 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Hands of angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:7-Ezek10:8\">EZK 10:7–10:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:15-1Chr21:16\">1CH 21:15–21:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:16\">2SA 24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:6\">ISA 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:8\">EZK 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Significant examples of hands</h2>\n<p>In Jacob's life:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:26\">GEN 25:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:16\">GEN 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:22-Gen27:23\">GEN 27:22–27:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:22\">EXO 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:21\">EXO 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:27\">EXO 14:27</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:17\">NEH 4:17</a> <em>Nehemiah's defences</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:23\">MAT 26:23</a> <em>Judas' betrayal</em></p>",
